要他打給我爸爸
Better yet,
have my father
talk to your father.

44
00:05:06,160 --> 00:05:07,218
我爸再打給你爸
Or my father
talk to your father.

45
00:05:10,698 --> 00:05:12,359
週末回家嗎？
You going home
this weekend, Chas?

46
00:05:13,434 --> 00:05:14,765
