羅絲太太！
Hi. Mrs. Rossi?
Yes?

67
00:06:53,067 --> 00:06:54,193
我是來應徵的
I'm here about
the weekend job.

68
00:06:57,004 --> 00:06:57,800
請進
Come on in.

69
00:07:02,676 --> 00:07:05,941
有沒有粉刺？他痛恨粉刺
Does he got pimples?
He hates pimples.

70
00:07:06,347 --> 00:07:07,746
