Francine, be quiet.

71
00:07:07,881 --> 00:07:10,543
粉刺，粉刺
Pimples.
Pimples. Yeah.

72
00:07:10,684 --> 00:07:11,673
噓…
Shush!

73
00:07:12,519 --> 00:07:14,885
