It's Charlie Simms.

75
00:07:16,357 --> 00:07:18,348
你好嗎？
好
How are you,
Charlie?
Fine, thanks.

76
00:07:18,559 --> 00:07:19,218
往這兒
Right this way.

77
00:07:23,630 --> 00:07:25,222
這週末都有空嗎？
You're available
the whole weekend?
Yeah.

78
00:07:27,301 --> 00:07:28,268
不回家過感恩節啊？
不
很好！
Not going home
for Thanksgiving?
No.
Good.

79
00:07:32,497 --> 00:07:35,022
