staggers a little
when he gets up,
don't pay
any attention.
Charlie,
I can tell you're
the right person for the job.

84
00:07:57,255 --> 00:08:03,650
法蘭克舅舅一定會喜歡你
你們要去哪裡
And Uncle Frank's
gonna like you a lot, too.
Where you gonna be
this weekend?

85
00:08:04,462 --> 00:08:05,861
開車回紐約
We're driving to Albany.

86
00:08:06,864 --> 00:08:10,598
唐尼…
我先生，他家在那兒
Donny, my husband,
has family there.

87
00:08:15,673 --> 00:08:17,334
要不要湯米出去？
Do you want
Tommy in or out?

88
00:08:17,475 --> 00:08:18,134
出去！
Leave him out!

89
00:08:18,943 --> 00:08:22,736
他又在追小野貓了…
從路頭追起呢
He's chasing that
Calico ginch from
the track houses again!

90
00:08:28,886 --> 00:08:31,411
其實他甜的跟糖似的
Down deep, the man
is a lump of sugar.

91
00:08:52,043 --> 00:08:52,702
長官？
Sir?

92
00:08:53,444 --> 00:08:54,968
少叫我「長官」
Don't call me sir.

93
00:08:55,513 --> 00:08:58,846
抱歉，我是說「先生」
長官
I'm sorry.
I mean mister, sir.

94
00:08:59,050 --> 00:09:02,577
啊！來了個白癡
不是嗎？
Uh-oh, we got a moron here,
is that it?

95
00:09:02,987 --> 00:09:09,716
不，先生，那…呃…
中尉，是的，長官，中…
No, mister...
That is...
Lieutenant.
Yes, sir...

96
00:09:09,794 --> 00:09:11,455
中校
Lieutenant Colonel.

97
00:09:12,196 --> 00:09:16,189
服役廿六年
