Twenty-six years on the line,
nobody ever busted me
four grades before.

98
00:09:17,068 --> 00:09:18,729
進來，笨蛋！
Get in here,
you idiot!

99
00:09:25,676 --> 00:09:28,474
靠近點，我要看清楚
Come a little closer.
I wanna get a
better look at you.

100
00:09:37,688 --> 00:09:38,882
