拿獎學金的，西門？
Simms, Charles.
A senior.
You on
student aid, Simms?

107
00:10:02,580 --> 00:10:03,569
是
Yes, I am.

108
00:10:04,248 --> 00:10:06,716
改叫「獎學金」為「罪犯」
