What are you, dying of
some wasting disease?

113
00:10:29,674 --> 00:10:31,471
沒有，我在這兒
No, I'm right...
I'm right here.

114
00:10:32,209 --> 00:10:34,734
我知道你站在哪兒
I know exactly where
your body is.

115
00:10:35,346 --> 00:10:38,213
我要的是個有腦子的看護
What I'm lookin' for
is some
indication of a brain.

116
00:10:39,417 --> 00:10:45,749
踢足球把腦子踢壞了？
詹森總統評福特總統
Too much football
without a helmet?
Hah! Lyndon's line
on Gerry Ford.

117
00:10:47,224 --> 00:10:50,625
我負責簡報
巴黎和談，1968
Deputy Debriefer, Paris,
Peace Talks, '66.

118
00:10:50,895 --> 00:10:54,892
