So, what are you doing here
in this sparrow-fart town?

134
00:11:41,145 --> 00:11:42,669
我念博德的
I attend Baird.

135
00:11:44,548 --> 00:11:46,209
念博德
Attend Baird!

136
00:11:47,551 --> 00:11:49,678
我知道你上博德
I know you go
to the Baird school.

137
00:11:50,154 --> 00:11:52,486
問題是，你怎麼上的起？
Point is,
how do you afford it,

138
00:11:53,357 --> 00:11:57,817
