1258
01:42:06,342 --> 01:42:08,207
對啊，給我信號
Yeah. Say when.

1259
01:42:08,477 --> 01:42:09,273
什麼？
Say when what?

1260
01:42:09,945 --> 01:42:10,934
轉彎信號
Say when to turn.

1261
01:42:11,146 --> 01:42:12,545
你不能轉彎
Colonel,
you can't turn the car.

1262
01:42:13,015 --> 01:42:14,539
在哪轉，查理？
Where's
the turn, Charlie?

1263
01:42:15,417 --> 01:42:18,614
三點鐘方位？兩點
右？歪？
3 o'clock? 2 o'clock?
Right oblique? Right face?

1264
01:42:18,754 --> 01:42:20,346
快啊，說啊
Come on! Talk to me!

1265
01:42:21,824 --> 01:42:22,882
左
It's left, I guess.

1266
01:42:23,158 --> 01:42:25,626
我知道轉左，現在？
Left. I knew it. Okay. Now?

1267
01:42:27,563 --> 01:42:29,155
不是不是！
No, no! Not now! Not now!

1268
01:42:30,733 --> 01:42:31,392
現在？
Now?

1269
01:42:32,434 --> 01:42:33,298
拜託
Colonel, please!

1270
01:42:33,502 --> 01:42:35,493
我要轉了
I'm gonna do it anyway,
all right?

1271
01:42:35,838 --> 01:42:37,567
不管你同不同意
Whether you say so
or not, here we go!

1272
01:42:37,706 --> 01:42:40,338
好，等等
等一下
Okay! Wait, wait, wait!
Just wait!

1273
01:42:40,409 --> 01:42:42,502
我要轉了…要轉了…
Here I go.

1274
01:42:42,711 --> 01:42:44,002
慢著
轉！
Wait... Now!

1275
01:42:51,053 --> 01:42:53,783
我轉成了！噢，查理！
I did it! Charlie!

1276
01:42:55,524 --> 01:42:57,651
你的同伴很快樂！
You're ridin' with
one very happy man!

1277
01:43:00,129 --> 01:43:01,061
你還得再轉
Turn again!

1278
01:43:01,330 --> 01:43:02,126
要仔細
Be specific, son.

1279
01:43:03,432 --> 01:43:04,228
向左，轉！
Left now!
Okay.

1280
01:43:10,873 --> 01:43:13,797
愛死這遊戲了！
愛死了！
I love this! I love it!

1281
01:43:15,210 --> 01:43:16,541
試試最高速
Shall we take it to the max?

1282
01:43:17,146 --> 01:43:18,135
我要下車
Let me out.

1283
01:43:21,083 --> 01:43:22,744
媽的！條子
Shit!
The yellow flag.

1284
01:43:23,752 --> 01:43:26,414
我還沒開始衝呢
I haven't even
opened her up yet.
Which way's the curb?

1285
01:43:26,822 --> 01:43:29,290
靠邊停，放慢，中校
Pull over. Slow down!
Slow down.

1286
01:43:29,358 --> 01:43:30,347
好吧，來了
I'm doin' it.

1287
01:43:30,426 --> 01:43:32,485
放慢
Pull over to
the curb, here.
Slow down.

1288
01:43:32,695 --> 01:43:33,491
我知道
Yep. Got it.

1289
01:43:47,242 --> 01:43:48,903
我幾年來都沒拿罰單
Haven't had
a ticket in years.

1290
01:43:52,848 --> 01:43:54,042
我來應付
I'll do the talking.

1291
01:44:00,389 --> 01:44:01,788
駕照和車牌
License
and registration.

1292
01:44:14,670 --> 01:44:15,932
在試這部小寶貝？
Are you test-driving
this baby?

1293
01:44:16,739 --> 01:44:17,865
很神吧？
Don't she purr, though?

1294
01:44:19,008 --> 01:44:20,475
時速七十英哩？
At 70 miles an hour?

1295
01:44:21,076 --> 01:44:23,067
你該看看她一百廿五的英姿
You should hear
her at 125.

1296
01:44:25,214 --> 01:44:26,545
駕照呢？
Where's your license?

1297
01:44:28,751 --> 01:44:32,414
在車行
還車的時候才拿
At the dealer's.
They give it back
when you return the car.

1298
01:44:33,956 --> 01:44:35,082
你有身份證？
You got ID?

1299
01:44:35,491 --> 01:44:36,287
可不是
You bet.

1300
01:44:38,360 --> 01:44:39,349
在此
Indeed.

1301
01:44:43,632 --> 01:44:45,429
史雷德中校
Lieutenant Colonel Slade.

1302
01:44:46,235 --> 01:44:47,361
你呢，警員？
And you, soldier?

1303
01:44:48,771 --> 01:44:51,239
我是高爾警官
The name is
Police Officer Gore.

1304
01:44:53,042 --> 01:44:54,703
你執勤認真
Doin' a hell
of a job, Gore.

1305
01:44:55,244 --> 01:44:56,905
你也不差，中校
And so are you,
Colonel.

1306
01:44:58,414 --> 01:44:59,346
小孩是誰？
Who's the kid?

1307
01:45:00,916 --> 01:45:02,247
小犬，查理
My boy Charlie.

1308
01:45:02,851 --> 01:45:06,787
一直叫我開她出來
能讓他失望嗎？
He kept tellin' me
to "let her out."
What was I gonna do,
disappoint him?

1309
01:45:07,656 --> 01:45:08,452
當然
Yes.

1310
01:45:12,695 --> 01:45:14,026
這麼辦吧…
Tell you what
I'm gonna do,
Colonel.

1311
01:45:14,730 --> 01:45:17,221
我放你一馬，但有個條件
I'm gonna let you go,
on one condition.

1312
01:45:17,733 --> 01:45:18,529
什麼？
What's that?

1313
01:45:19,268 --> 01:45:21,998
馬上把車送回車行
That you take this rig
straight back to the dealer.

1314
01:45:24,339 --> 01:45:25,328
沒問題
You got it.

1315
01:45:25,741 --> 01:45:26,730
閉嘴
Shut up.

1316
01:45:27,943 --> 01:45:28,932
要這個嗎？
You want this?

1317
01:45:29,678 --> 01:45:30,406
當然
Sure.

1318
01:45:32,081 --> 01:45:32,877
高爾
Gore?

1319
01:45:34,216 --> 01:45:36,480
你的臉孔和聲音我很熟
Your face and
your voice
are familiar.

1320
01:45:36,852 --> 01:45:38,843
加入過丹納的軍官俱樂部嗎？
You ever been
in the officer's
club at Da Nang?

1321
01:45:40,456 --> 01:45:41,115
沒有
No.

1322
01:45:41,790 --> 01:45:42,779
也沒進過陸軍
Never in the Army?

1323
01:45:44,760 --> 01:45:46,091
沒有，海岸防衛隊而已
No. Coast Guard.

1324
01:45:46,962 --> 01:45:47,951
老天
Good Lord.

1325
01:45:53,969 --> 01:45:55,834
你爸氣色不錯，查理
Your dad
is looking good,
Charlie.

1326
01:45:56,238 --> 01:45:59,571
就是喜歡開快車…
勸他開慢點
He's got a heavy foot, though.
Tell him to take it light,
all right?

1327
01:46:01,176 --> 01:46:02,507
知道了
I hear ya!
All right.
Thanks.

1328
01:46:17,192 --> 01:46:20,457
下車，不准你再開了
Get out of the car,
because you are not
driving anymore.

1329
01:46:20,529 --> 01:46:22,520
我在暖車罷了
Just keeping this baby
warm, that's all.

1330
01:46:25,134 --> 01:46:26,601
我不開了
I'm not drivin' anymore.
Yes.

1331
01:46:38,280 --> 01:46:40,145
扶著我的肩膀
Take my arm.
I'm okay.

1332
01:46:40,415 --> 01:46:41,882
路不平
Colonel,
it's really
bumpy here.

1333
01:46:56,765 --> 01:46:57,754
還好吧？
You all right?
Yeah.

1334
01:47:11,113 --> 01:47:13,104
紅燈，中校，別走
Red light. Hold it.

1335
01:47:19,521 --> 01:47:20,385
等太久了
Taking too long.
Shit! Colonel! Colonel!
Colonel!

1336
01:47:40,209 --> 01:47:41,540
沒事吧？
Shit! You all right?

1337
01:47:43,212 --> 01:47:46,204
你幹什麼你？拿好拐杖啊
What the hell
are you doing?
Take the cane.

1338
01:47:46,415 --> 01:47:48,542
我要尿尿
拿好拐杖
I gotta take a piss.
Take the cane.

1339
01:47:48,617 --> 01:47:49,811
小便不能忍
Happens to
the best of us.

1340
01:47:49,885 --> 01:47:53,343
不能在公園大道尿啊
最好不過
We're on
Park Avenue.
You can't.
Perfect place.

1341
01:47:54,156 --> 01:47:55,487
警察會抓你的
You'll get arrested.

1342
01:47:55,891 --> 01:47:57,222
我從來不亂尿
Never been
housebroken.
Colonel!
Shit!

1343
01:48:00,429 --> 01:48:02,090
你到底怎麼搞的？
What's the matter
with you, Colonel?

1344
01:48:09,238 --> 01:48:12,404
你在幹嘛？
快起來
What are you doing?
Stand up.

1345
01:48:13,842 --> 01:48:14,831
別亂來
Come on.

1346
01:48:15,310 --> 01:48:17,642
我好累，查理
I'm tired, Charlie.
I'm tired.

1347
01:48:20,115 --> 01:48:21,309
讓我握你手臂
Give me your arm.

1348
01:48:22,517 --> 01:48:23,506
你的拐杖
Here's your cane.

1349
01:48:25,520 --> 01:48:27,249
帶我回旅館，孩子
Take me back
to the hotel, son.

1350
01:48:33,784 --> 01:48:34,910
總算到家了
Home at last.

1351
01:48:56,807 --> 01:48:57,796
你還好吧？
You all right now?
Yeah.

1352
01:49:05,482 --> 01:49:07,211
要不要上廁所？
Do you want to
use the bathroom?

1353
01:49:07,685 --> 01:49:08,344
不要
No.

1354
01:49:18,028 --> 01:49:20,019
需要什麼嗎？
不要
Can I get you
something?
No.

1355
01:49:24,835 --> 01:49:27,167
你真的沒事？
我很好
You sure you're
all right?
I'm fine, Charlie.

1356
01:49:46,523 --> 01:49:47,854
我可以打電話嗎？
Do you mind if
I use the phone?

1357
01:49:48,859 --> 01:49:49,848
打吧
Go ahead.
Hello?

1358
01:50:10,614 --> 01:50:11,945
請問喬治在嗎？
Hi, is George there,
please?

1359
01:50:12,483 --> 01:50:13,472
小喬還是老喬？
Senior or Junior?

1360
01:50:15,686 --> 01:50:16,482
小喬
Junior.

1361
01:50:17,021 --> 01:50:18,010
哪位？
Who's this?

1362
01:50:18,689 --> 01:50:20,213
他學校的朋友
A friend of his
from school.

1363
01:50:20,291 --> 01:50:24,625
他不能跟任何朋友講話了
Sorry, but George isn't going
to be talking to any friends
from school right now.
Oh.
Goodbye.

1364
01:50:46,583 --> 01:50:48,107
你在瞪我嗎？
Colonel, are you
looking at me?

1365
01:50:51,655 --> 01:50:53,054
我是個瞎子，查理
I'm blind, Charlie.

1366
01:50:59,730 --> 01:51:01,254
我要去睡一會兒
I'm gonna take a nap.

1367
01:51:04,401 --> 01:51:05,595
兜風太久
Too much fresh air.

1368
01:51:08,072 --> 01:51:09,403
那好
It's probably a good idea.

1369
01:51:10,808 --> 01:51:12,139
我扶你進房
Want me to help you
to your room?

1370
01:51:13,811 --> 01:51:14,800
不必
No.

1371
01:51:16,213 --> 01:51:17,202
我睡沙發
Couch.

1372
01:51:18,549 --> 01:51:20,210
我喜歡這張
I like this couch here.

1373
01:51:23,754 --> 01:51:25,745
你真的沒事？
You sure you're
all right, Colonel?

1374
01:51:26,090 --> 01:51:27,216
我頭痛
I got a headache.

1375
01:51:34,098 --> 01:51:37,090
下樓去替我買阿斯匹靈吧
Why don't you go
downstairs, get me
some aspirin?

1376
01:51:37,167 --> 01:51:40,500
好
另外…
Some aspirin.
Yeah. Also...

1377
01:51:43,307 --> 01:51:44,638
再帶根雪茄
I feel like a cigar.

1378
01:51:46,443 --> 01:51:50,971
蒙地奎斯特一號的
Get me a couple of
Montecristos Number One.

1379
01:51:51,048 --> 01:51:52,913
蒙地奎斯特一號
Montecristos
Number One.
Yeah.

1380
01:51:53,517 --> 01:51:55,849
樓下小店不會有
You won't be able
to get 'em at
the newsstand downstairs.

1381
01:51:56,453 --> 01:51:58,114
那你就過街…
So why don't you
go over to

1382
01:51:59,323 --> 01:52:01,791
到街口的唐喜商店買
50th and Fifth,
Dunhill's.

1383
01:52:02,526 --> 01:52:05,051
叫阿諾的在掌櫃
Fella named Arnold there,
in the humidor.

1384
01:52:06,330 --> 01:52:09,322
告訴他是我要的
Tell him
they're for me.

1385
01:52:10,334 --> 01:52:11,323
他知道的
He'll know.

1386
01:53:00,588 --> 01:53:02,249
回來的太快了吧？
You're back
too fast.

1387
01:53:05,526 --> 01:53:07,517
你一定沒替我買雪茄？
You didn't get
my cigars, did you?

1388
01:53:13,067 --> 01:53:14,398
滾開，查理
Get out of
here, Charlie.

1389
01:53:19,473 --> 01:53:20,804
我們已經講清楚了
I thought we had a deal.

1390
01:53:22,009 --> 01:53:26,137
我毀約
我愛毀約，沒告訴過你？
I welched.
I'm a welcher.
Didn't I tell you?

1391
01:53:27,514 --> 01:53:29,982
你說要把所有子彈給我
No, what you told me
was that you gave me
all the bullets.

1392
01:53:31,285 --> 01:53:32,411
騙你的
I lied.

1393
01:53:34,421 --> 01:53:35,888
你是把我騙住了
You could have fooled me.

1394
01:53:36,290 --> 01:53:37,348
可不是
And I did.

1395
01:53:40,561 --> 01:53:44,019
沒有我，你怎麼辦啊？
How you ever
gonna survive in this
world without me?

1396
01:53:48,802 --> 01:53:50,997
把槍給我好嗎？
Why don't you just
give me the gun,
all right?

1397
01:54:00,714 --> 01:54:02,045
你幹什麼？
What are you doing?

1398
01:54:04,184 --> 01:54:06,243
我也會一槍打死你
I'm gonna
shoot you, too.

1399
01:54:09,390 --> 01:54:11,051
反正你已經完了
Your life's
finished anyway.

1400
01:54:12,726 --> 01:54:16,924
喬治會見風轉舵
你也一樣完蛋
Your friend George
is going to sing
like a canary.
And so are you.

1401
01:54:17,331 --> 01:54:19,799
一旦如此，查理寶寶…
And once you've sung,
Charlie, my boy,

1402
01:54:20,200 --> 01:54:24,330
你在那乏味的成人隊伍中
you're gonna take
your place on that
long, gray line

1403
01:54:24,405 --> 01:54:26,202
就佔有一席之地了…
of American manhood.

1404
01:54:27,875 --> 01:54:29,866
你也就完了
And you will
be through.

1405
01:54:32,012 --> 01:54:33,411
我不苟同
I'd like to disagree
with you, Colonel.

1406
01:54:33,647 --> 01:54:39,385
你沒資格不苟同
四五手槍在我手裡
你只有粉刺
You're in no
position to disagree
with me, boy.
I got a loaded.45 here.
You got pimples.

1407
01:54:40,354 --> 01:54:42,015
我要把你殺了…
I'm gonna
kill ya, Charlie,

1408
01:54:42,823 --> 01:54:44,916
因為我不能忍受看著你去…
because I can't
bear the thought

1409
01:54:45,025 --> 01:54:46,151
出賣原則
of you sellin' out!

1410
01:54:48,562 --> 01:54:50,689
把槍放下
Put the gun down,
all right, Colonel?

1411
01:54:51,098 --> 01:54:52,087
什麼？
你在下最後通牒？
What? You givin' me
an ultimatum?
No, I'm...

1412
01:54:57,504 --> 01:54:59,495
最後通牒由我來下！
I give the ultimatums!

1413
01:55:01,108 --> 01:55:02,097
抱歉
I'm sorry.

1414
01:55:04,211 --> 01:55:05,872
我道歉
All right? I'm sorry.

1415
01:55:09,383 --> 01:55:10,714
我也道歉
It's all right,

1416
01:55:12,519 --> 01:55:13,508
查理
Charlie.

1417
01:55:18,659 --> 01:55:20,320
你傷了我的心，孩子
You break
my heart, son.

1418
01:55:22,262 --> 01:55:24,059
我這一生…
All my life
I stood up

1419
01:55:25,065 --> 01:55:27,397
反抗任何人，所有事…
to everyone
and everything,

1420
01:55:28,402 --> 01:55:32,494
只有這樣，我才覺得…
自己重要
because it made me
feel important.

1421
01:55:34,608 --> 01:55:37,475
但你卻是為了
你的原則而反抗
You do it
'cause you mean it.

1422
01:55:40,214 --> 01:55:41,943
你很正直
You got
integrity, Charlie.

1423
01:55:46,220 --> 01:55:49,417
我不曉得該打死你
還是收養你
I don't know whether to
shoot you or adopt you.

1424
01:55:52,426 --> 01:55:54,223
很為難，是吧？
Not much of a choice,
is it, sir?

1425
01:55:54,762 --> 01:55:57,094
少耍嘴皮子
Don't get cute now.

1426
01:55:57,431 --> 01:55:59,160
請把槍放下
Could you please
put the gun away?

1427
01:55:59,433 --> 01:56:00,764
我在問你問題
I asked you
a question.

1428
01:56:01,769 --> 01:56:04,431
你要不要我收養你？
Do you want me
to adopt you,
or don't you?

1429
01:56:05,773 --> 01:56:06,899
請放下槍…
Please? I mean...

1430
01:56:08,909 --> 01:56:10,900
你只是情緒低落
You're just in a slump
right now.

1431
01:56:11,645 --> 01:56:12,634
情緒低落？
Slump?

1432
01:56:15,315 --> 01:56:16,976
不是，查理
No slump, Charlie.

1433
01:56:19,453 --> 01:56:20,784
我是壞人
I'm bad.

1434
01:56:23,791 --> 01:56:25,452
不，我不很壞
I'm not bad. No.

1435
01:56:28,328 --> 01:56:29,317
我爛掉了
I'm rotten.

1436
01:56:33,133 --> 01:56:34,122
你不壞
You're not bad.

1437
01:56:37,871 --> 01:56:39,532
只是痛苦而已
You're just in pain.

1438
01:56:45,546 --> 01:56:47,537
你懂什麼叫痛苦？
What do you know
about pain?

1439
01:56:51,351 --> 01:56:55,811
你只不過是大海裡的一隻小魚
You little snail darter
from the Pacific Northwest.

1440
01:56:57,157 --> 01:56:59,148
你媽的懂什麼叫痛苦？
Fuck you know
about pain?

1441
01:57:02,763 --> 01:57:04,230
把槍給我
Let me have the gun,
Colonel.

1442
01:57:05,365 --> 01:57:07,492
