02:26:06,371 --> 02:26:08,032
很濫情吧？
How's that
for cornball?

1769
02:26:29,861 --> 02:26:31,852
摀不住他們嘴巴的，先生
Nothing can
shut them up, sir.

1770
02:26:36,335 --> 02:26:41,329
生活委員會將再開會討論此案
The disciplinary
committee will take
this matter under advisement
in closed session.

1771
02:26:49,815 --> 02:26:51,476
他們在幹嘛？
What are they doin',
Charlie?
I think they're
going to come to
a decision now.
Very well.

1772
02:27:06,031 --> 02:27:08,693
很顯然的，不必再開會了
Apparently, that meeting
will be unnecessary.

1773
02:27:09,768 --> 02:27:11,099
杭賽克太太
Mrs. Hunsaker.

1774
02:27:15,574 --> 02:27:20,443
生活委員會不必另行開會
The joint student-faculty
disciplinary committee
needs no further sessions.

1775
02:27:20,846 --> 02:27:22,837
他們已達成決議
They have come to a decision.

1776
02:27:23,582 --> 02:27:26,449
海夫曼爾、波特
及詹姆森先生
Messrs. Havemeyer,
Potter and Jameson

1777
02:27:26,518 --> 02:27:31,512
因涉嫌不當作為
而留校查看
are placed on probation
for suspicion of
ungentlemanly conduct.

1778
02:27:31,790 --> 02:27:34,953
另外建議
喬治威利斯二世先生
It is further recommended
that Mr. George Willis, Jr.

1779
02:27:35,027 --> 02:27:40,363
不因其合作而做任何表揚或處分
Receive neither recognition
nor commendation
for his cooperation.

1780
02:27:41,666 --> 02:27:46,535
西門先生將不需
為此事件負責
Mr. Charles Simms is excused
from any further response
to this incident.
Hoo-ah!
Charlie!

1781
02:28:47,532 --> 02:28:50,865
小心！
有你在我很放心
Last step.
I can always count
on you, Charlie.

1782
02:28:54,606 --> 02:28:57,598
中校…
Colonel!

1783
02:28:59,544 --> 02:29:02,877
我是克莉絲汀.唐伊
政治學教授
I'm Christine Downes,
Colonel Slade.
I teach
political science.

1784
02:29:03,148 --> 02:29:06,481
非常感謝您的高見
I wanted to tell you
how much I appreciate
you speaking your mind.

1785
02:29:06,551 --> 02:29:07,950
謝謝，你結婚了？
Why, thank you.
Are you married?
I...

1786
02:29:13,491 --> 02:29:17,086
我在炮兵課的同學
也姓唐伊
Went to an artillery school
at Fort Sill with
a Mickey Downes.

1787
02:29:17,162 --> 02:29:18,220
我以為他釣上你了
Thought he might've
snagged you.

1788
02:29:18,897 --> 02:29:20,888
沒有呢
No, I'm afraid not.

1789
02:29:22,767 --> 02:29:25,964
史中校曾是詹森的幕僚
Colonel Slade was on
Lyndon Johnson's staff,
Miss Downes.

1790
02:29:26,705 --> 02:29:28,764
真的？太精彩了
Were you? Fascinating.

1791
02:29:29,040 --> 02:29:31,565
有空我們應該聊聊政治
We should get together,
talk politics sometime.

1792
02:29:35,513 --> 02:29:36,707
芙洛兒.狄蘿卡里絲香水
Fleurs de Rocaille.

1793
02:29:39,184 --> 02:29:40,173
正是！
Yes.

1794
02:29:41,986 --> 02:29:43,578
「小溪之花」
"Flowers from a brook."

1795
02:29:45,590 --> 02:29:46,921
對
That's right.

1796
02:29:51,062 --> 02:29:54,463
唐伊小姐
我知道到哪找你
Well, Miss Downes,
I'll know where to find you.
Charlie.
Bye, Miss Downes.
Bye.

1797
02:30:04,275 --> 02:30:06,266
你不必告訴我
You don't have to
tell me, Charlie.

1798
02:30:07,345 --> 02:30:08,676
五尺七
5'7",

1799
02:30:10,148 --> 02:30:11,809
赤鳶色髮
auburn hair,

1800
02:30:12,884 --> 02:30:33,973
美麗的棕色大眼
beautiful brown eyes.

1801
02:30:33,973 --> 02:30:35,304
呀吧嗒吧嘟！
Yabba-dabba-doo.
Manny.

1802
02:30:44,316 --> 02:30:45,647
太多了
Colonel, this
is too much.

1803
02:30:45,718 --> 02:30:50,121
你應得的
下次查理和我去紐約時
會再找你，你帶我們來回
Never mind,
you earned it.
Next time Charlie and I
want to take a
breather to New York,
we're gonna call you.
You can drive us
both ways.

1804
02:30:53,793 --> 02:30:57,991
沒問題，中校，我的榮幸
我給您打折
You're on,
Colonel.
Not only will it
be an honor,
I'll give you
a rate.

1805
02:30:58,264 --> 02:30:59,458
我再加倍給小費
I'll see your rate
and raise you.

1806
02:31:01,000 --> 02:31:02,797
保重
Stay outta
harm's way, Manny.

1807
02:31:03,002 --> 02:31:04,993
保重，中校
你也一樣
Take care,
Colonel.
You, too.

1808
02:31:06,472 --> 02:31:08,463
不，謝了，我自己走
Ready?
No. I'll take it
from here.

1809
02:31:09,742 --> 02:31:13,075
走吧，曼尼會送你回宿舍
You go on ahead.
Manny'll drive you
to your dorm.

1810
02:31:14,814 --> 02:31:18,341
聖誕節前再來
咱倆喝一杯
Come by before you
go home for Christmas.
We'll have a little cheer.

1811
02:31:19,752 --> 02:31:22,084
你要是願意，就留下晚餐
And if you like,
stay for dinner.

1812
02:31:22,288 --> 02:31:26,622
有時候她做燒雞
還能入口
Sometimes she cooks
a pot roast.
It's almost edible.

1813
02:31:28,494 --> 02:31:29,825
好，中校
All right, Colonel.
That'd be really...

1814
02:31:30,696 --> 02:31:31,890
那會是…
再見，查理
Bye, Charlie.

1815
02:31:52,518 --> 02:31:53,849
是誰？
是你嗎，法蘭絲？
Who's there?
That you, Francine?
Yes.

1816
02:31:57,323 --> 02:32:00,315
你在做什麼？
騎車
What are you doing?
Taking a ride.

1817
02:32:00,526 --> 02:32:03,791
讓我搭便車吧？
Taking a ride?
What about you
giving me a lift?

1818
02:32:04,864 --> 02:32:05,592
不要
No.

1819
02:32:06,065 --> 02:32:07,054
不要？
No?

1820
02:32:07,666 --> 02:32:13,061
拜託嘛，法蘭絲
我們重歸於好嘛
你不想跟我和我？
Come on, Francine.
We should make up.
Don't you think
it's time we made up?

1821
02:32:13,672 --> 02:32:14,536
不想
No.
Francine?
What?

1822
02:32:16,475 --> 02:32:22,478
你法蘭克叔公過了一個
很辛苦的…
感恩節週末
Uncle Frank's had
a really hard
Thanksgiving weekend.

1823
02:32:23,549 --> 02:32:24,208
那是什麼？
我聽到花栗鼠
還是海象？
What's that?
I hear a chipmunk.
Is it a walrus?

1824
02:32:28,954 --> 02:32:30,285
都不是，是威利
No, it's Willie.

1825
02:32:30,823 --> 02:32:38,689
要不要幫我拿提袋？
來嘛！乖
來吧
Willie, why don't you
help me with my bag?
Come on, son.
Help me with my bag.
Come on. Come on.

1826
02:32:39,098 --> 02:32:41,896
拿好了？拿穩哦
走
You got it. Hold onto it.
You're strong. Come on.
Here we are.

1827
02:32:47,773 --> 02:32:50,105
跟我和威利來
Francine, come on
with me and Willie.

1828
02:32:50,643 --> 02:32:54,443
你可以請我吃巧克力
好不好
I'll let you make me
some marshmallow
chocolate.
What do you say?
Good!

